Information
------------------------------

The Coolest Places on Earth 
The Coolest Places on Earth takes viewers on a journey of discovery to the most astonishing places on the planet - cities, festivals, landmarks and jaw-dropping works of nature - exploring each location's history and culture, to discover why it deserves to be called one of the coolest places on earth!




10)  Australia 
Today on The Coolest Places on Earth: We're heading down under to one of the coolest continents on earth...Australia! We'll go surfing and sunbathing on Sydney's amazing beaches, cross the legendary outback, and get to the bottom...and the top of Uluru. We'll also get an earful from the cockatoos on Kangaroo island. It's going to be a bonzer time!
